<font face="Trebuchet MS">All right?</font>

934
01:17:40,560 --> 01:17:42,561
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Okay.</font>

935
01:17:43,560 --> 01:17:48,087
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You need to get a tracking number.
With alerts to my cell phone.</font>

936
01:17:49,760 --> 01:17:52,285
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- Yeah.
- All right.</font>

937
01:17:52,320 --> 01:17:54,560
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Thanks.</font>

938
01:17:58,800 --> 01:18:00,801
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Wait.</font>

939
01:18:05,080 --> 01:18:06,919
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Tell your mother
it was very good.</font>

940
01:18:06,920 --> 01:18:08,719
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah?</font>

941
01:18:08,720 --> 01:18:10,926
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Not too salty?</font>

942
01:18:11,120 --> 01:18:12,679
<font face="Trebuchet MS">No.</font>

943
01:18:12,680 --> 01:18:15,364
<font face="Trebuchet MS">It was perfect.</font>

944
01:18:36,480 --> 01:18:38,679
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Hey, this shit's coming together.
(PICKUP TRUCK DOOR CLOSES)</font>

945
01:18:38,680 --> 01:18:40,679
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Paul was definitely here.</font>

946
01:18:40,680 --> 01:18:41,959
<font face="Trebuchet MS">How'd you know he was here?</font>

947
01:18:41,960 --> 01:18:43,439
<font face="Trebuchet MS">The manager.</font>

948
01:18:43,440 --> 01:18:45,159
<font face="Trebuchet MS">He asked for this.</font>

949
01:18:45,160 --> 01:18:48,159
<font face="Trebuchet MS">It's a list of all
the people buried here.</font>

950
01:18:48,160 --> 01:18:51,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS">The guy said he was more interested
in the Hungarian section.</font>

951
01:18:52,480 --> 01:18:55,439
<font face="Trebuchet MS">The Hungarian section.
Did he say why?</font>

952
01:18:55,440 --> 01:18:57,487
<font face="Trebuchet MS">No.</font>

953
01:18:57,920 --> 01:18:59,967
<font face="Trebuchet MS">There's hundreds of them.</font>

954
01:19:13,240 --> 01:19:15,366
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Ah.</font>

955
01:19:16,720 --> 01:19:18,881
<font face="Trebuchet MS">What happened to that girl?</font>

956
01:19:20,200 --> 01:19:23,359
<font face="Trebuchet MS">That girl you told me about
across the way from you.</font>

957
01:19:23,360 --> 01:19:25,441
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You ever meet her?</font>

958
01:19:25,800 --> 01:19:28,404
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah. I met her.</font>

959
01:19:29,280 --> 01:19:31,281
<font face="Trebuchet MS">And?</font>

960
01:19:36,840 --> 01:19:40,320
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You didn't die two years ago.</font>

961
01:19:48,880 --> 01:19:51,325
<font face="Trebuchet MS">They found the cemetery.</font>

962
01:19:53,600 --> 01:19:56,045
<font face="Trebuchet MS">They're getting close.</font>

963
01:19:56,280 --> 01:19:58,964
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(THUNDER CRASHES)</font>

964
01:20:00,720 --> 01:20:02,881
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(GROANS)</font>

965
01:20:03,280 --> 01:20:05,519
<font face="Trebuchet MS">The one who found
you before got lucky.</font>

966
01:20:05,520 --> 01:20:07,439
<font face="Trebuchet MS">And just because
he found the grave</font>

967
01:20:07,440 --> 01:20:11,523
<font face="Trebuchet MS">doesn't mean that they will
figure it out as well.</font>

968
01:20:12,000 --> 01:20:14,240
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You can walk away, still.</font>

969
01:20:14,680 --> 01:20:17,091
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Not too late.</font>

970
01:20:18,240 --> 01:20:22,119
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I know why you've
been waiting so long.</font>

971
01:20:22,120 --> 01:20:25,122
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Why you haven't killed him.</font>

972
01:20:25,320 --> 01:20:29,802
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I think you're afraid
that when it's over,</font>

973
01:20:30,040 --> 01:20:32,883
<font face="Trebuchet MS">it won't mend your heart.</font>

974
01:20:38,520 --> 01:20:41,522
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(<i>LIFE IN MONO</i> PLAYING)</font>

975
01:20:46,080 --> 01:20:48,650
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(SPEAKING FRENCH)</font>

976
01:20:56,240 --> 01:20:57,799
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(EXCLAIMS)</font>

977
01:20:57,800 --> 01:20:59,759
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You're beautiful.</font>

978
01:20:59,760 --> 01:21:05,119
<font face="Trebuchet MS">It was going to waste.
I just felt like putting it on.</font>

979
01:21:05,120 --> 01:21:07,199
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I know why you put it on.</font>

980
01:21:07,200 --> 01:21:08,279
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Or should I say,</font>

981
01:21:08,280 --> 01:21:10,327
<font face="Trebuchet MS">...for whom.</font>

982
01:21:16,320 --> 01:21:18,845
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- Hey, monster!
- Hey!</font>

983
01:21:21,880 --> 01:21:23,881
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Get out of here!
Come on!</font>

984
01:21:24,040 --> 01:21:26,121
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(EXCLAIMS IN DISAPPOINTMENT)</font>

985
01:21:34,800 --> 01:21:37,450
<font face="Trebuchet MS">What... What happened?</font>

986
01:21:39,240 --> 01:21:44,370
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- I fell and ruined a nice dress.
- Let me see.</font>

987
01:21:46,320 --> 01:21:48,481
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You Okay?</font>

988
01:21:49,400 --> 01:21:50,799
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah.</font>

989
01:21:50,800 --> 01:21:54,167
<font face="Trebuchet MS">At least it
wasn't my good side.</font>

990
01:21:57,640 --> 01:21:59,199
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I sent your package.</font>

991
01:21:59,200 --> 01:22:02,199
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I have your
tracking number.</font>

992
01:22:02,200 --> 01:22:03,319
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Thank you.</font>

993
01:22:03,320 --> 01:22:05,039
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- Hello, Victor.
- Hello.</font>

994
01:22:05,040 --> 01:22:06,719
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Go take off your dress,
it's covered in blood.</font>

995
01:22:06,720 --> 01:22:09,609
<font face="Trebuchet MS">He shouldn't
see you like this.</font>

996
01:22:16,520 --> 01:22:19,759
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- Thank you for returning my Tupperware.
- Of course.</font>

997
01:22:19,760 --> 01:22:23,684
<font face="Trebuchet MS">People usually don't.
Like it comes with the food.</font>

998
01:22:24,400 --> 01:22:26,679
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Free Tupperware.
(LAUGHS)</font>

999
01:22:26,680 --> 01:22:28,886
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Did you like the food?</font>

1000
01:22:29,160 --> 01:22:31,519
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah. The food was...</font>

1001
01:22:31,520 --> 01:22:34,010
<font face="Trebuchet MS">It was very good.
Beatrice didn't tell you?</font>

1002
01:22:34,040 --> 01:22:37,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS">She was nervous you
wouldn't like her cooking.</font>

1003
01:22:42,960 --> 01:22:47,567
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I always told her the way to a man's
heart is through his stomach.</font>

1004
01:22:48,240 --> 01:22:50,890
<font face="Trebuchet MS">One of the ways.</font>

1005
01:22:51,120 --> 01:22:54,487
<font face="Trebuchet MS">She'll keep you well fed.
That's for sure.</font>

1006
01:23:05,400 --> 01:23:08,919
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You know, this thing, me
falling and hitting my head?</font>

1007
01:23:08,920 --> 01:23:13,402
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Maybe it happened because
I lost my rabbit's foot.</font>

1008
01:23:16,560 --> 01:23:20,079
<font face="Trebuchet MS">The truth is my mom gave it
to me after the accident.</font>

1009
01:23:20,080 --> 01:23:24,084
<font face="Trebuchet MS">She said it was going to bring
me luck with my procedures.</font>

1010
01:23:25,640 --> 01:23:27,399
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I picked the colour.</font>

1011
01:23:27,400 --> 01:23:30,084
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Stupid chartreuse.</font>

1012
01:23:33,800 --> 01:23:36,131
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(ELEVATOR DOORS OPENING)</font>

1013
01:23:37,400 --> 01:23:39,401
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Hey.</font>

1014
01:23:42,200 --> 01:23:45,282
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Would you go out
with me tonight?</font>

1015
01:23:47,280 --> 01:23:49,520
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Somewhere.</font>

1016
01:23:50,160 --> 01:23:52,161
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Anywhere.</font>

1017
01:23:53,360 --> 01:23:55,119
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah.</font>

1018
01:23:55,120 --> 01:23:57,121
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Okay.</font>

1019
01:24:18,600 --> 01:24:21,125
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(CHILDREN LAUGHING)</font>

1020
01:24:38,080 --> 01:24:41,560
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(CELL PHONE VIBRATES)</font>

1021
01:24:52,960 --> 01:24:55,564
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- Yeah.
DARCY: <i>Laszlo Kerik.</i></font>

1022
01:24:58,040 --> 01:25:00,690
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Laszlo Kerik?
You know the name?</font>

1023
01:25:01,480 --> 01:25:04,679
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- No. No, I don't know him.
- I didn't think you would.</font>

1024
01:25:04,680 --> 01:25:08,759
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I've been searching every dead
Hungarian on this cemetery list.</font>

1025
01:25:08,760 --> 01:25:12,399
<font face="Trebuchet MS">This shit went down about nine
months before we were on the crew.</font>

1026
01:25:12,400 --> 01:25:15,399
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>There was a case involving
Alphonse and a little girl</i></font>

1027
01:25:15,400 --> 01:25:18,039
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>Who was killed in
one of his buildings.</i></font>

1028
01:25:18,040 --> 01:25:20,319
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>The case never went to
trial. Get this, right?</i></font>

1029
01:25:20,320 --> 01:25:22,559
<font face="Trebuchet MS">The little girl's
mommy and daddy,</font>

1030
01:25:22,560 --> 01:25:24,079
<font face="Trebuchet MS">they died,
like, two months afterwards.</font>

1031
01:25:24,080 --> 01:25:26,491
<font face="Trebuchet MS">They're buried
right there next to her.</font>

1032
01:25:29,840 --> 01:25:32,046
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>Vic?</i></font>

1033
01:25:32,560 --> 01:25:35,608
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You there? Vic? Vic?</font>

1034
01:25:36,160 --> 01:25:37,959
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- Yeah. I'm here.
- <i>I did it, man.</i></font>

1035
01:25:37,960 --> 01:25:39,719
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I fucking did it.</font>

1036
01:25:39,720 --> 01:25:43,039
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I found out exactly what
Paul must have found out.</font>

1037
01:25:43,040 --> 01:25:45,759
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>Look, I want to tell Alphonse. I want
you to be there when I tell him.</i></font>

1038
01:25:45,760 --> 01:25:47,439
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>Can you get there?</i></font>

1039
01:25:47,440 --> 01:25:52,161
<font face="Trebuchet MS">No, I'm in the middle of something.
I'll talk to you later.</font>

1040
01:26:12,040 --> 01:26:14,246
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(KNOCKING ON DOOR)</font>

1041
01:26:18,080 --> 01:26:19,519
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Oh, Victor.</font>

1042
01:26:19,520 --> 01:26:22,879
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I didn't know you were coming. I
would have thrown something on.</font>

1043
01:26:22,880 --> 01:26:24,679
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>Maman</i>, you knew very
well he was coming.</font>

1044
01:26:24,680 --> 01:26:25,919
<font face="Trebuchet MS">No, you didn't
tell me anything.</font>

1045
01:26:25,920 --> 01:26:28,279
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Well, I told you so.</font>

1046
01:26:28,280 --> 01:26:30,281
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(BOTH SPEAKING FRENCH)</font>

1047
01:26:30,440 --> 01:26:32,805
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- Ready?
- Mmm-hmm.</font>

1048
01:26:40,440 --> 01:26:42,441
<font face="Trebuchet MS">So...</font>

1049
01:26:43,480 --> 01:26:44,639
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Where are we going?</font>

1050
01:26:44,640 --> 01:26:46,766
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You'll see.</font>

1051
01:26:48,960 --> 01:26:50,961
<font face="Trebuchet MS">A club?</font>

1052
01:26:51,040 --> 01:26:52,279
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Very cold.</font>

1053
01:26:52,280 --> 01:26:53,959
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(LAUGHS)</font>

1054
01:26:53,960 --> 01:26:56,291
<font face="Trebuchet MS">A park?</font>

1055
01:27:01,880 --> 01:27:03,319
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Are you okay?</font>

1056
01:27:03,320 --> 01:27:05,560
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah. Good.</font>

1057
01:27:22,320 --> 01:27:24,810
<font face="Trebuchet MS">- This is...
- The bar.</font>

1058
01:27:25,640 --> 01:27:27,839
<font face="Trebuchet MS">In his house,
some credit card receipts.</font>

1059
01:27:27,840 --> 01:27:31,359
<font face="Trebuchet MS">He usually leaves the bar at 8:30 every night.
But he took a trip.</font>

1060
01:27:31,360 --> 01:27:32,959
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I want to
make sure he's back.</font>

1061
01:27:32,960 --> 01:27:37,169
<font face="Trebuchet MS">If he's here tonight, he'll
probably be here tomorrow night.</font>

1062
01:27:42,880 --> 01:27:46,008
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I'm prepared to do it then.</font>

1063
01:27:57,200 --> 01:27:59,406
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I...</font>

1064
01:28:00,280 --> 01:28:04,045
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I've found a moment with you.</font>

1065
01:28:07,640 --> 01:28:10,130
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I want to hang onto it.</font>

1066
01:28:13,880 --> 01:28:16,564
<font face="Trebuchet MS">It's not gonna
end up that way.</font>

1067
01:28:20,560 --> 01:28:22,879
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I never said it would.</font>

1068
01:28:22,880 --> 01:28:25,211
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Not with words.</font>

1069
01:28:35,080 --> 01:28:38,287
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I wore that
white dress for you.</font>

1070
01:28:39,560 --> 01:28:41,891
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Was that a mistake?</font>

1071
01:28:51,680 --> 01:28:53,761
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yes.</font>

1072
01:29:04,920 --> 01:29:08,400
<font face="Trebuchet MS">All right, wait here.
I'll be back in a minute.</font>

1073
01:30:17,840 --> 01:30:20,205
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(PANTING)</font>

1074
01:30:22,200 --> 01:30:24,850
<font face="Trebuchet MS">What did you do?</font>

1075
01:30:28,040 --> 01:30:30,280
<font face="Trebuchet MS">It's done.</font>

1076
01:30:30,360 --> 01:30:31,799
<font face="Trebuchet MS">It's done.</font>

1077
01:30:31,800 --> 01:30:34,245
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(CAR ENGINE STARTING)</font>

1078
01:31:13,760 --> 01:31:15,886
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(CAR DOOR CLOSES)</font>

1079
01:31:36,080 --> 01:31:38,079
<font face="Trebuchet MS">One, two.</font>

1080
01:31:38,080 --> 01:31:40,081
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Nope.</font>

1081
01:31:40,400 --> 01:31:42,526
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Uh-uh.</font>

1082
01:31:42,600 --> 01:31:45,443
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Hold up. It's this one.</font>

1083
01:31:48,760 --> 01:31:50,439
<font face="Trebuchet MS">So you're saying
it's someone who knew them?</font>

1084
01:31:50,440 --> 01:31:52,439
<font face="Trebuchet MS">He must have.</font>

1085
01:31:52,440 --> 01:31:55,090
<font face="Trebuchet MS">'Cause this guy's dead, right?</font>

1086
01:31:57,440 --> 01:31:59,441
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Right?</font>

1087
01:31:59,840 --> 01:32:01,839
<font face="Trebuchet MS">(MUTTERING)</font>

1088
01:32:01,840 --> 01:32:04,171
<font face="Trebuchet MS">What is it?</font>

1089
01:32:04,200 --> 01:32:07,931
<font face="Trebuchet MS">The little girl
died June 17th.</font>

1090
01:32:08,000 --> 01:32:10,365
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Two years ago. Right?</font>

1091
01:32:10,800 --> 01:32:12,881
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah.</font>

1092
01:32:13,120 --> 01:32:16,009
<font face="Trebuchet MS">June 17th is tomorrow.</font>

1093
01:32:48,680 --> 01:32:51,091
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Beatrice.</font>

1094
01:32:51,240 --> 01:32:53,526
<font face="Trebuchet MS">What are you doing?</font>

1095
01:32:57,960 --> 01:32:59,399
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Oh, my God.</font>

1096
01:32:59,400 --> 01:33:01,039
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Beatrice!</font>

1097
01:33:01,040 --> 01:33:02,719
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.</font>

1098
01:33:02,720 --> 01:33:03,999
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I'm sorry. I'm sorry.</font>

1099
01:33:04,000 --> 01:33:06,126
<font face="Trebuchet MS">What?</font>

1100
01:33:20,400 --> 01:33:23,846
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah, I'm walking
back to him now. Okay.</font>

1101
01:33:29,480 --> 01:33:30,799
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah.</font>

1102
01:33:30,800 --> 01:33:32,519
<font face="Trebuchet MS">ALPHONSE: <i>Hey, you know
who this is, right?</i></font>

1103
01:33:32,520 --> 01:33:34,119
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah, I know who it is.</font>

1104
01:33:34,120 --> 01:33:37,519
<font face="Trebuchet MS">I've been getting these weird
letters for the last three months.</font>

1105
01:33:37,520 --> 01:33:39,679
<font face="Trebuchet MS">With pictures?
With the eyes crossed out?</font>

1106
01:33:39,680 --> 01:33:41,279
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>I've been getting them, too.</i></font>

1107
01:33:41,280 --> 01:33:43,725
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Whoever is doing it
took my brother.</font>

1108
01:33:48,680 --> 01:33:54,561
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You remember this problem
I had you take care of for me?</font>

1109
01:33:55,520 --> 01:33:58,039
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>Hungarian Rhapsody?</i></font>

1110
01:33:58,040 --> 01:33:59,719
<font face="Trebuchet MS">You stayed to the finale.
Right?</font>

1111
01:33:59,720 --> 01:34:01,839
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>Yeah.</i></font>

1112
01:34:01,840 --> 01:34:04,319
<font face="Trebuchet MS">And the whole
family took a bow?</font>

1113
01:34:04,320 --> 01:34:05,519
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Yeah.</font>

1114
01:34:05,520 --> 01:34:09,251
<font face="Trebuchet MS">And you're sure you saw
the father take a bow?</font>

1115
01:34:11,280 --> 01:34:13,839
<font face="Trebuchet MS">DARCY ON PHONE: <i>Where the fuck have you been?
I've been trying to call you.</i></font>

1116
01:34:13,840 --> 01:34:15,519
<font face="Trebuchet MS">My car won't start.</font>

1117
01:34:15,520 --> 01:34:16,959
<font face="Trebuchet MS">Some shit's
going down, man.</font>

1118
01:34:16,960 --> 01:34:18,319
<font face="Trebuchet MS"><i>The fucking thing
won't start.</i></font>

